&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mandatory Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4+ years of experience&lt;/strong&gt; in media planning, strategy, or marketing analytics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Deep TV &amp;amp; Streaming Expertise:&lt;/strong&gt; Proven experience building and executing impactful plans across linear TV, streaming/CTV, and audio channels.&lt;/li&gt;
