&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Will Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Saatva is seeking an operational, strategic, and results-driven &lt;strong&gt;Talent Acquisition Manager&lt;/strong&gt; to evolve our recruitment function. As we scale our physical footprint and customer service operations, we need an optimization champion who can take us to the next level with incredible efficiency.&lt;/p&gt;
